WEBVTT

00:00:01.834 --> 00:00:05.574
KALETET MISPAR SHTAYIM, Lev Rozov.

00:00:07.234 --> 00:00:09.970
der rus iz arayn bay aykh...

00:00:09.090 --> 00:00:14.860
itster nayn un draysikter yor: di rusn zaynen arayn bay undz un m'hot ongehoybn makhn valn

00:00:14.860 --> 00:00:16.782
oyf a, oyf a,

00:00:16.782 --> 00:00:21.574
oyf shikn un- shikn undz in Byalistok, iz geven ⟨a rusishe,⟩ oyf dem,

00:00:21.574 --> 00:00:23.785
az me zol zey untershraybn

00:00:23.785 --> 00:00:26.880
az mir viln zikh fareynikn mit Rusland.

00:00:28.210 --> 00:00:30.940
m'hot aykh gebetn untertsushraybn?

00:00:29.998 --> 00:00:32.090
⟨y- ot, ye,⟩ ikh'l aykh dertseyln.

00:00:32.090 --> 00:00:34.042
hot men gemakht valn

00:00:34.487 --> 00:00:37.080
un m'hot geklibn, mir hot men oysgeklibn

00:00:37.542 --> 00:00:39.810
un ikh bin geforn in Byalistok.

00:00:40.174 --> 00:00:44.319
m'hot gemakht dortn in Byalistok, zey hobn shoyn undz gegebn a...

00:00:44.545 --> 00:00:47.526
un vos zey zogn, dos hot men gedarft makhn.

00:00:48.088 --> 00:00:52.945
do hob ikh shoyn bamerkt, iz di zakh azoy, az me kon shoyn fun zey nit avekgeyn.

00:00:52.945 --> 00:00:56.253
ir kont nit makhn eygene zakhn vos ir trakht,

00:00:56.253 --> 00:00:58.140
zogn az ir trakht...

00:00:58.140 --> 00:00:59.810
vel ikh aykh oykh dertseyln

00:00:59.810 --> 00:01:02.360
vi azoy eyner hot gezogt az "ikh trakht"...

00:01:02.360 --> 00:01:04.840
a groyser komunist far di poyln gevezn...

00:01:04.840 --> 00:01:06.594
vos m'hot mit im gemakht.

00:01:07.866 --> 00:01:10.593
⟨m'iz ge⟩kumen. ikh bin oysgeklibn gevorn

00:01:11.342 --> 00:01:13.680
fun dem gants⟨n,⟩

00:01:13.680 --> 00:01:16.213
shtetl, fun UNK gantsn krayz.

00:01:16.489 --> 00:01:18.980
undz hot men avekgeshikt in Byalistok.

00:01:19.408 --> 00:01:22.760
zaynen mir tsuzamengeforn fun ale shtetlekh,

00:01:22.952 --> 00:01:25.173
i fun Vaysrusland,

00:01:25.399 --> 00:01:27.080
i fun Ukrayne...

00:01:27.137 --> 00:01:30.500
vayle Ukrayne iz dokh oykh geven unter Poyln a teyl.

00:01:30.500 --> 00:01:32.360
do hobn zey dokh oykh farnumen...

00:01:32.360 --> 00:01:33.943
fun di tsvey

00:01:33.943 --> 00:01:38.454
melukhes vos zaynen geven a teyl a mol shayekh tsu zey.'

00:01:38.578 --> 00:01:43.567
un m'hot undz genumen bay a tish ⟨un m'hot⟩ geredt, ⟨zaynen⟩ gekumen zeyere groyse mentshn

00:01:43.658 --> 00:01:45.840
fun tsenter, fun Moskeve.

00:01:45.840 --> 00:01:48.515
un mir hobn gedarft untershraybn zey

00:01:48.515 --> 00:01:49.980
az mir betn

00:01:50.290 --> 00:01:54.379
az zey zoln undz tsunemen tsu zi- tsu z- krik tsu ⟨R-⟩

00:01:54.379 --> 00:01:56.294
tsu di, tsu zey,

00:01:56.294 --> 00:02:01.725
vayle mir zaynen geven fa- unter a, unter a fremder makht zaynen mir gevezn.

00:02:02.119 --> 00:02:07.344
nu, hobn mir untergeshribn, dortn geven, m'hot farbrakht, un dortn... iz geven a zakh,

00:02:07.401 --> 00:02:09.960
epes a por vokhn geven dortn in gantsn,

00:02:09.966 --> 00:02:12.947
⟨un nokh dem bin ikh⟩ gekumen aheym. gekumen aheym...

00:02:13.155 --> 00:02:17.688
nu, vayter ongehoybn klaybn. bin ikh oysgeklibn IR- in IRIYA.

00:02:17.948 --> 00:02:19.629
ir v-... in shtot-rat.

00:02:19.703 --> 00:02:22.009
shtot-rat, ⟨hot men mir⟩ oysgeklibn

00:02:22.335 --> 00:02:26.429
in shtot-rat. nakher in shtot-rat bin ikh gezesn mit mentshn, bin ikh

00:02:26.655 --> 00:02:31.180
far a prezide- far a prezes fun shtot-rat. nor vos?

00:02:31.180 --> 00:02:34.560
der hoypt-prezes hobn zey geshikt,

00:02:34.560 --> 00:02:37.148
vayle mir veysn nit vos tsu makhn.

00:02:37.148 --> 00:02:38.550
ir farshteyt?

00:02:38.550 --> 00:02:41.516
zey hobn shoyn genumen alts oyf zeyer zayt.

00:02:42.147 --> 00:02:43.510
UNK

00:02:43.510 --> 00:02:47.780
m'hot ongehoybn yemolt... dos iz shoyn geven bald fertsikter yor.

00:02:47.867 --> 00:02:51.500
⟨nayn un dray- dos, ikh bin⟩ avekgegangen, geven fertsikter yor...

00:02:51.500 --> 00:02:55.960
fertsikter yor hobn ongehoybn firn vi zey viln.

00:02:56.035 --> 00:02:59.030
me hot opgenumen di mil,

00:02:59.157 --> 00:03:01.001
der ⟨za-⟩... di tsveyte zakh,

00:03:01.001 --> 00:03:07.469
hobn zey opgenumen, genumen fanand, tsugenumen dem bir-zavod fun shtot in gantsn.

00:03:07.662 --> 00:03:10.710
hob ikh zikh geshtelt... ikh bin dokh a ⟨UNK⟩ediker...

00:03:10.710 --> 00:03:14.060
zogt er, "oyf vos darft ir a bir⟨UNK⟩ in shtot? ir hot azoy fil,

00:03:14.060 --> 00:03:17.173
fir toyznt mentshn; mir veln aykh tsushteln bir vifl ir vet darfn."

00:03:17.753 --> 00:03:18.928
ir farshteyt?

00:03:19.002 --> 00:03:21.673
un m'hot, eyner hot zikh geshtelt gegn.

00:03:21.673 --> 00:03:27.297
m'hot im arestirt. m'hot im tsugenumen ⟨un⟩ gezogt, er iz a natsyonalist UNK a vaysrus.

00:03:28.300 --> 00:03:29.728
m⟨'hot oyf im gem-⟩...

00:03:28.688 --> 00:03:31.350
iz der vos hot zikh, der vos hot z-

00:03:29.937 --> 00:03:31.871
 der vos hot zikh gegngeshtelt.

00:03:31.350 --> 00:03:35.567
gegngeshtelt gegn vos m'hot gezogt fun Moskve, hot men oyf enk...

00:03:32.907 --> 00:03:36.910
UNK ⟨ot⟩ vos m'hot gevolt tsunemen, dos iz er shoyn a natsyonalist;

00:03:36.910 --> 00:03:38.773
er hert nit vos zey zogn.

00:03:40.585 --> 00:03:41.814
ir farshteyt?

00:03:41.814 --> 00:03:45.810
"s'iz nito bay undz," zogn zey, "keyn natsyonalistn. mir zaynen ale eyn mishpokhe."

00:03:48.313 --> 00:03:50.006
⟨es⟩ iz nit azoy geven.

00:03:50.006 --> 00:03:52.745
di lage iz gevorn an andere,

00:03:52.819 --> 00:03:57.203
di atmosfer iz gevorn an andere. ikh hob ongehoybn trakhtn vos me trakht,

00:03:57.203 --> 00:04:02.400
iz di ershte zakh, mayn oyfgabe iz geven, m'hot, ye, un m'iz ongefaln oyf undz fun zeyer,

00:04:02.400 --> 00:04:04.338
fun di rusishe zayt...

00:04:04.750 --> 00:04:06.805
s'iz dokh oyfn grenets...

00:04:06.805 --> 00:04:10.270
un me hot oysgekoyft alts fun di gesheftn.

00:04:11.670 --> 00:04:17.011
⟨a-⟩ alts, fun a zok biz a ⟨l-⟩... vegn broyt redt zikh nit.

00:04:17.017 --> 00:04:20.200
m'hot ts- tsenumen az mir hobn nit gehat vos tsu esn.

00:04:20.325 --> 00:04:21.669
di gantse broyt.

00:04:21.861 --> 00:04:24.810
bin ikh, UNK...

00:04:23.768 --> 00:04:26.560
far vos hobn zey ales oysgekoyft? zey hobn gehat,

00:04:25.354 --> 00:04:27.831
vayle dortn iz gornisht nit ge-...

00:04:26.560 --> 00:04:28.318
dort iz gornisht geven?

00:04:27.831 --> 00:04:31.460
bay zey iz gornisht nit geven. ot, ikh'l aykh dertseyln:

00:04:31.460 --> 00:04:34.630
az ikh hob shoyn bay zey gearbet, klingt mir eyne on,

00:04:34.630 --> 00:04:36.969
vos arbet oykh in a, in Minsk.

00:04:36.969 --> 00:04:39.253
klingt zi on: "shik mir a por shikh."

00:04:39.293 --> 00:04:42.920
zog ikh, "velkhe numer?" ikh freg ⟨i-⟩ bay ir UNK...

00:04:42.920 --> 00:04:44.484
zogt zi, "KHOT' KAKOY!"

00:04:45.030 --> 00:04:48.310
iz dos iz, "khotsh velkhe numer, nor shikh!"

00:04:46.743 --> 00:04:47.880
UNK

00:04:48.310 --> 00:04:51.369
iz shtelt zikh for vos far a folk es iz gevezn;

00:04:51.915 --> 00:04:55.880
ayeder hot nit gevust avos far a numer shikh zi trogt.

00:04:56.944 --> 00:04:59.780
ikh hob shoyn, az zi zogt mir, "KHOT' KAKOY!"

00:04:59.780 --> 00:05:04.548
iz, iz hob ikh shoyn ongehoybn trakhtn, "vos iz dortn, a mentsh tsi nit a mentsh?"

00:05:04.723 --> 00:05:10.060
u- un a yunge m- a, a, a meydl, a yunge meydl, gearbet dortn oyf a sekretarke.

00:05:10.060 --> 00:05:11.850
parteyne, zey zaynen

00:05:11.850 --> 00:05:16.085
dokh dortn geshikt tsu, dortn geshikt parteyne mentshn, komunistn.

00:05:16.085 --> 00:05:18.860
iz ⟨ze ikh m-⟩ iz "KHOT' KAKOY!" iz, iz,

00:05:18.860 --> 00:05:21.221
iz ze ikh dokh shoyn mit vemen me hot tsu ton.

00:05:21.919 --> 00:05:23.299
ikh bin geven,

00:05:23.299 --> 00:05:27.982
ikh bin geven a durkhgetribener yingl a mol, nit azoy, getrakht.

00:05:27.982 --> 00:05:32.950
nor ikh hob nit ge- ikh hob nit gekont reydn. ikh bin geven shoyn in N.K.V.D. gezesn oykh UNK ⟨nit⟩.

00:05:32.950 --> 00:05:34.553
me hot shoyn mir dernokh dem,

00:05:34.710 --> 00:05:36.710
shoyn nokh di krig gevezn.

00:05:37.866 --> 00:05:47.890
neyn, zey hobn ongehoybn azoy firn. nu, ongehoybn firn, un di mil hot men tsugenumen. iz gekumen tsu mir der balebos fun mil, der mil- der balebos fun mil,

00:05:47.890 --> 00:05:50.651
mir zoln im gebn vo- fun vos tsu lebn.

00:05:50.995 --> 00:05:57.160
iz di yugntlekhe tsugekumen ⟨tsu im,⟩ hobn zey gezogt, "fort avek in Vileyke. fort aroys fun danet,

00:05:57.272 --> 00:05:58.930
vu me kon aykh nit."

00:05:59.263 --> 00:06:01.349
⟨iz a⟩ khevre gelernte.

00:06:03.685 --> 00:06:06.860
"fort aroys in Vileyke." iz geven bay undz

00:06:06.860 --> 00:06:09.174
lebn Vil-... in Vilne hobn zey nit geratn...

00:06:09.174 --> 00:06:11.570
lebn Vilne, in di klenere shtetlekh:

00:06:11.570 --> 00:06:14.259
"fort aroys un ordnt zikh ayn oyf arbet un arbet!

00:06:16.358 --> 00:06:19.590
vayl oto do, az m'vet aykh konen, vet nit toygn."

00:06:19.598 --> 00:06:21.530
iz vos hobn mentshn getun?

00:06:21.083 --> 00:06:25.298
UNK un me hot geheysn haltn ofn di kromen, on a frage,

00:06:25.298 --> 00:06:29.837
oder az s'iz nit geven, keyn tsugefirte skhoyre iz nit geven,

00:06:29.837 --> 00:06:31.724
iz vos iz geven in di kromen?

00:06:32.507 --> 00:06:34.260
gornisht! a, nit...

00:06:34.260 --> 00:06:39.234
zey voltn koyfn a zakh vos dos hot men gedarft aroysvarfn... gib ikh aykh... un zey voltn dos koyfn!

00:06:39.443 --> 00:06:42.470
zey hobn nit gevust gornisht. zey hobn gornisht nit gehat.

00:06:42.470 --> 00:06:45.540
aza oremkeyt! ikh bin ⟨d-⟩ nakher umgeforn,

00:06:45.540 --> 00:06:49.562
hob ikh gezen a oremkeyt. az tsu mir iz gekumen eyn mol

00:06:50.040 --> 00:06:54.470
der PREDSEDATEL' VERKHOVNOGO SOVETA,

00:06:54.715 --> 00:06:56.990
dos heyst fun Minsk,

00:06:57.195 --> 00:06:58.758
zogt er tsu mir...

00:06:59.507 --> 00:07:02.610
gekumen... ikh bin shoyn geven mit di froy tsuzamen.

00:07:02.610 --> 00:07:05.660
in fertsik, vi d- zey zaynen gekumen, hob ikh glaykh khasene gehat,

00:07:05.660 --> 00:07:08.107
vayle di ershte yorn hob ikh gelebt in hotel,

00:07:08.198 --> 00:07:10.841
hob ikh gelebt, glaykh dortn avekgegangen lebn.

00:07:11.185 --> 00:07:16.400
un ikh hob shoyn zikh geboyt a dire. ikh hob zikh gemakht ⟨a dire⟩. iz ⟨z-⟩...

00:07:15.302 --> 00:07:17.709
ven hot ir zikh geboyt a dire?

00:07:17.192 --> 00:07:18.020
ven...?

00:07:17.732 --> 00:07:18.907
ven hot ir...?

00:07:18.020 --> 00:07:21.600
⟨a, d- v-⟩ ot in UNK in fertsiktn yor

00:07:21.600 --> 00:07:23.818
hot men genumen boyen a klub.

00:07:24.364 --> 00:07:28.290
genumen boyen a klub. dos iz alts, ikh bin geven ⟨PO KHOZYAY-⟩

00:07:28.290 --> 00:07:30.562
oyf di ar- oto di ale zakhn:

00:07:30.562 --> 00:07:34.320
mestn vi, ver hot a groyse shtub un ver es hot a kleyne shtub,

00:07:34.320 --> 00:07:37.330
bay vemen kon men opnemen a shtub. ikh gib aykh a bayshpil, di...

00:07:37.330 --> 00:07:39.599
s'iz dokh shoyn geven an ander VLAST'.

00:07:39.599 --> 00:07:42.650
nit ikh, nor me hot mir geshikt umetum.

00:07:42.650 --> 00:07:44.692
hot men mir geshikt a inzhenyer.

00:07:45.373 --> 00:07:51.594
iz gekumen der inzhenyer un genumen boyen a shtub. iz dortn bay undz geshtanen epes nit keyn farendikte shtub, keynem,

00:07:51.702 --> 00:07:53.622
fun a mol a poylish⟨e⟩ UNK.

00:07:53.622 --> 00:07:55.307
hob ikh ir genumen, geendikt,

00:07:55.397 --> 00:07:59.981
un m'hot ir oysgemolt. ikh bin arayn lebn ahin, vayle ikh bin dokh shoyn geven mit di froy.

00:07:59.278 --> 00:08:02.000
un mit vem hot ir khasene gehat?

00:08:00.949 --> 00:08:03.255
in fertsiktn yor nayyor.

00:08:03.784 --> 00:08:07.642
nayn un draysik, ot dos iz geven nayyor hob ikh khasene gehat, ⟨oyf fe-⟩...

00:08:06.830 --> 00:08:08.824
mit vemen? vi azoy hot...?

00:08:07.665 --> 00:08:11.320
mit der zelber meydl vos ikh bin umgegangen ale yor.

00:08:11.320 --> 00:08:13.396
ikh hob nit gezukht keyn andere.

00:08:13.521 --> 00:08:17.143
⟨ikh,⟩ ikh bin nit... un far vos hob ikh glaykh khasene gehat?

00:08:13.740 --> 00:08:15.708
vi hot zi geheysn?

00:08:17.233 --> 00:08:20.315
s'hobn zikh on-... ikh'l aykh zogn: ikh bin geven a man,

00:08:20.322 --> 00:08:23.693
a yung⟨er⟩, nit azoy ⟨z-⟩... hot eyne a mol, volt eyne kumen

00:08:23.693 --> 00:08:28.216
nekhtikn un di andere kumen nekhtikn. ikh ze az ikh hob fun zey keyn ba- keyn, nit,

00:08:28.216 --> 00:08:30.750
un ikh hob moyre gehat mit zey tsu hobn gesheft.

00:08:30.750 --> 00:08:34.590
undzere hobn moyre gehat mit zey tsu hobn gesheftn,

00:08:34.590 --> 00:08:37.174
vayl dos iz a folk... afile yidn.

00:08:37.179 --> 00:08:39.310
ikh'l aykh dertseyln a epizod

00:08:39.310 --> 00:08:40.910
fun a yidn fun dem

00:08:40.910 --> 00:08:42.467
komunistishe partey.

00:08:42.467 --> 00:08:46.910
⟨iz bin ikh⟩ khasene gehat mit ir. vi azoy mir hobn khasene gehat,

00:08:46.910 --> 00:08:49.510
tsuzamengeklibn mayne eygene khaveyrim,

00:08:50.207 --> 00:08:51.663
mayne eygene,

00:08:51.663 --> 00:08:56.580
un m'hot mir mekadesh geven, ongeton a fingerl un khasene gehat. v⟨os⟩ UNK...

00:08:55.450 --> 00:08:57.930
vi azoy hot geheysn ayer froy?

00:08:57.328 --> 00:08:58.928
a, f-, Gite.

00:08:58.923 --> 00:09:00.030
GITA?

00:08:58.928 --> 00:09:02.503
dos iz GENYA, itster heyst zi GENYA in di dokumentn.

00:09:02.188 --> 00:09:03.751
GENYA GITA.

00:09:02.560 --> 00:09:06.200
⟨G-⟩ GENYA, GENYA Levitan, ir fami-...

00:09:04.990 --> 00:09:06.452
Levitan?

00:09:06.200 --> 00:09:08.600
Levitan. fun, oykh a Dokshitser.

00:09:08.582 --> 00:09:09.920
oykh fun Doksh-...

00:09:08.600 --> 00:09:10.450
zey hobn gehat a bekeray.

00:09:10.450 --> 00:09:13.061
bay zey iz di mishpokhe um⟨ge-⟩... o! zey hobn gehat

00:09:13.061 --> 00:09:17.415
shvester khasene-gehate. zi iz geven... un gor di yingste hob ikh getrofn do.

00:09:17.308 --> 00:09:19.765
di yi- zi iz geven di ying-...?

00:09:17.415 --> 00:09:20.205
eyne. ⟨iz zi⟩ oder oykh geshtorbn.

00:09:20.869 --> 00:09:25.030
di, gor d- gor di yingste shvester iz UNK oykh antlofn.

00:09:25.105 --> 00:09:28.900
nor ikh hob ir in Rusland nit gevust, nor ikh bin gekumen aher, hot zi ⟨d-⟩

00:09:28.900 --> 00:09:30.653
durkh, durkh SOKHNUT

00:09:30.653 --> 00:09:32.118
hot zi mir gefunen.

00:09:32.496 --> 00:09:34.410
do in Erets-Yisroel shoyn?

00:09:32.580 --> 00:09:33.930
UNK

00:09:33.930 --> 00:09:36.630
do, oto do. iz ire tsvey kinder iz do.

00:09:36.630 --> 00:09:39.335
iz zi volt kumen tsu undz oyf peysekh, m⟨UNK⟩ mit ir...

00:09:39.335 --> 00:09:43.640
ikh'l aykh zogn azoy: bay mir iz dokh geborn gevorn a kind. az⟨oy volt ikh⟩ mit ir ⟨avekgeyn lebn⟩.

00:09:43.640 --> 00:09:45.520
s'iz der man irer geharget gevorn.

00:09:45.520 --> 00:09:46.921
s'iz oykh tragedyes.

00:09:46.921 --> 00:09:49.280
dos iz ale azetike zakhn vos

00:09:49.280 --> 00:09:52.100
me kon nit, me kon alts nit dertseyln.

00:09:52.100 --> 00:09:55.004
s'iz azetike tragedye⟨s⟩, me zol dos nemen dertseyln,

00:09:55.004 --> 00:09:57.970
iz oyf eyn mol ⟨k-⟩ makht ⟨men dos⟩ nit.

00:09:57.970 --> 00:10:03.330
nu, ikh bin gekumen tsu ir un ikh hob ge- un zi hot geveynt, dos, ⟨gebi-⟩ gebitn di dire, hob ikh ir geholfn.

00:10:03.377 --> 00:10:06.276
un, un ire kleyne kinder iz bay ir geven.

00:10:06.276 --> 00:10:10.762
iz, iz, iz UNK zey oyf ale yontoyvim nemen tsu undz.

00:10:12.000 --> 00:10:16.410
iz nayntsn fertsik hot ir khasene gehat mit...

00:10:14.818 --> 00:10:17.680
in fer- in fertsiktn yor UNK...

00:10:16.410 --> 00:10:19.940
nayntsn fertsik hot ir khasene gehat...

00:10:17.680 --> 00:10:19.132
nayntsn fertsik.

00:10:19.257 --> 00:10:21.413
 ye, ikh hob khasene gehat,

00:10:21.413 --> 00:10:22.898
un mir hobn genumen lebn.

00:10:22.898 --> 00:10:24.640
in eyn un fertsik

00:10:24.825 --> 00:10:26.928
iz bay mir geborn gevorn der zun.

00:10:27.576 --> 00:10:31.367
iz der zun geborn gevorn. hobn mir gemakht dem bris.

00:10:32.503 --> 00:10:34.252
gemakht a bris.

00:10:34.579 --> 00:10:41.420
fun UNK geven der foter, der foter iz geven sandek, ⟨iz⟩ dortn ⟨nokh⟩ geven bay mir der moyel, der rov,

00:10:41.420 --> 00:10:44.056
un mir hobn gemakht nokh abi shoyn far di Sovyetn.

00:10:44.417 --> 00:10:46.183
un ikh hob gearbet in IRIYA,

00:10:46.290 --> 00:10:48.309
hob ikh nokh shoyn dan gearbet.

00:10:48.771 --> 00:10:54.215
iz hob ikh, hob⟨n mir⟩ gemakht dem bris, un afile di froy hot zikh ongehoybn filn nit gut,

00:10:54.357 --> 00:10:57.800
nor, nor s'iz gevorn alts beser un mir hobn gelebt normal.

00:10:57.800 --> 00:11:02.410
ir muter volt undz trogn di esns, un zi ho- ir hot men glaykh an arbet gegebn.

00:11:02.410 --> 00:11:04.320
zi hot gearbet far a,

00:11:04.320 --> 00:11:08.208
far a onfirerke fun a PI- fun a PIV⟨NYARYA,⟩ aza mit

00:11:08.208 --> 00:11:12.060
tey, vu me trinkt, aza, ⟨dortn a-⟩ aza gesheft.

00:11:12.060 --> 00:11:13.690
dos gemakht di ershte...

00:11:13.690 --> 00:11:18.820
in Dokshits iz a mol geven, nor bay yenem hot men dos genumen, hot men ir avekgeshtelt, zi zol firn.

00:11:18.820 --> 00:11:21.230
zi hot gehat a por mentshn un zi hot UNK...

00:11:21.230 --> 00:11:22.666
un zey voltn kumen.

00:11:22.842 --> 00:11:25.750
vil ikh aykh zogn az di, di hoypt-firer

00:11:25.750 --> 00:11:30.270
voltn kumen, der betn shokolad, der volt betn dos, ⟨der...⟩ un zey voltn tsien.

00:11:30.270 --> 00:11:34.969
iz dos shoyn nokh alts geven di rezervn fun shtetl.

00:11:35.987 --> 00:11:38.440
vos m'hot gehat fun farn krig.

00:11:37.590 --> 00:11:41.340
fu- ye, dos iz ale rezervn vos mir hobn gehat farn krig.

00:11:42.113 --> 00:11:44.655
vi azoy hot geheysn dos kind?

00:11:44.442 --> 00:11:45.215
ver?

00:11:45.215 --> 00:11:48.240
di kind? di kind hot geheysn Mendele,

00:11:45.235 --> 00:11:46.700
ayer kind.

00:11:48.240 --> 00:11:52.502
Mendl. er iz do, iz do in bikhl vos ikh hob ge⟨UNK⟩ UNK.

00:11:52.542 --> 00:11:58.890
Mendl, un der, nor UNK in, in di papir farshribn Maks., es iz dokh shoyn geven

00:11:58.890 --> 00:12:01.480
a, a rusishe atmosfere,

00:12:01.480 --> 00:12:05.985
shoyn ⟨geven an andere⟩. ikh heys, gerufn hot men mir Leybe, Leyb,

00:12:06.430 --> 00:12:10.000
un farshribn hobn zey Lev un dos iz geblibn Lev.

00:12:10.210 --> 00:12:13.326
un do hob ikh shoyn tsugeshribn Arye.

00:12:13.635 --> 00:12:19.029
Arye hob ikh shoyn ⟨ge⟩⟨UNK⟩. vayle in fabrik hot men mir, vu ikh hob do gearbet, hot men mir gerufn Arye.

00:12:14.339 --> 00:12:15.900
Leyb iz Arye.

00:12:18.006 --> 00:12:19.080
Arye.

00:12:19.086 --> 00:12:21.341
UNK

00:12:20.267 --> 00:12:27.073
ir hot gevust,... di rusn zenen geven bay enk; ir hot gevust vos s'tut zikh in Poyln oyf d-...

00:12:25.347 --> 00:12:26.320
nor...

00:12:27.073 --> 00:12:32.090
ir hot gevust vos s'tut zikh in Poyln vos s'iz bazetst fun Daytshland?

00:12:30.173 --> 00:12:32.895
⟨ne-⟩ o! itster azoy: tsu u-

00:12:32.895 --> 00:12:35.410
tsu undz iz shoyn gekumen yidishe yugntlekhe.

00:12:35.410 --> 00:12:37.500
UNK ⟨volt men⟩ gekumen in shul,

00:12:37.500 --> 00:12:41.040
⟨un m'iz gekum-...⟩ fu- meydlekh mit yinglekh, yunge khevre.

00:12:40.298 --> 00:12:42.490
fun vanet fun Poyln?

00:12:41.040 --> 00:12:45.410
fun Poyln. fun Poyln. fun velkhe shtet kon ikh nit zogn,

00:12:43.186 --> 00:12:44.890
antlofn?

00:12:45.410 --> 00:12:49.060
nor dortn iz shoyn geven der daytsh, iz zaynen zey shoyn tselofn.

00:12:49.060 --> 00:12:51.220
hobn zey... nokh nit geven keyn,

00:12:51.220 --> 00:12:54.890
zet ir nokh, az zey zaynen gekumen iz nokh keyn getos nit geven,

00:12:54.890 --> 00:12:56.820
nor zey hobn ongehoybn zogn

00:12:56.820 --> 00:12:59.574
az me traybt tsuzamen di yidn in eyn ort.

00:12:59.574 --> 00:13:01.892
z- mir hobn nit gevust vos s'heyst "geto."

00:13:02.185 --> 00:13:04.260
fun vanet hobn mir gevust vos ⟨s'iz "g-"...?⟩ ikh hob,

00:13:04.260 --> 00:13:06.262
kh'hob dos nit gehert, vos s'iz "geto."

00:13:06.454 --> 00:13:09.190
ikh hob nit gevust vos far a nomen dos iz "geto."

00:13:09.190 --> 00:13:12.950
m'hot ts- di yidn traybt men tsuzamen. di khevre hobn dertseylt, di yidn

00:13:12.950 --> 00:13:15.680
⟨vos zaynen ge⟩kumen tsu mir. ⟨m'⟩volt zey gebn esn, un volt zey d⟨o-...⟩

00:13:15.680 --> 00:13:18.370
der hoypt zaynen zey geven in shul, volt der foter kumen

00:13:18.370 --> 00:13:23.947
zogn vos der tay- vos der daytsh, der daytsh, shlogt shoyn yidn un me harget un me traybt.

00:13:24.308 --> 00:13:25.837
UNK...

00:13:24.696 --> 00:13:26.971
un dos hot men enk dertseylt?

00:13:26.971 --> 00:13:31.080
zey zenen, zey zenen gekumen alts FLÜCHTLINGE fun...?

00:13:29.910 --> 00:13:32.789
zey zaynen gekumen oyf tsu loyfn dem grenets.

00:13:32.813 --> 00:13:36.587
iberlo- ibergelofn di grenets in Rusland arayn?

00:13:33.724 --> 00:13:36.286
ibergelofn di grenets keyn Rusland,

00:13:36.286 --> 00:13:39.260
vayle bay undz iz geven di grenets, hobn zey gemuzt kumen,

00:13:39.260 --> 00:13:44.400
undzer shtetl, vayle keyn an- zey hobn gehat dortn a veg vu azoy tsu geyn tsu di rusn.

00:13:44.369 --> 00:13:47.622
un vos hobn zey dertseylt, az me harget yidn?

00:13:46.330 --> 00:13:49.420
az me harget nokh, hobn zey nokh nit dertseylt.

00:13:49.420 --> 00:13:52.440
zey hobn nor dertseylt vos me traybt tsuzamen yidn,

00:13:52.440 --> 00:13:57.810
un me lozt yidn ergets nit arbetn, ⟨,⟩ di groyse mentshn, lerer, di... dortn iz dokh geven

00:13:57.810 --> 00:14:00.960
UNK ⟨es⟩ makht zikh

00:14:00.960 --> 00:14:03.789
a s- a samatokhe tsevishn di yidn.

00:14:04.723 --> 00:14:09.410
dos iz nokh geven frier, eyder d- dos zaynen geven nokh afile eyder di rusn ⟨zay-⟩

00:14:09.410 --> 00:14:12.372
zaynen tsu undz gekumen, zaynen shoyn geven khevre. eyder!

00:14:12.372 --> 00:14:14.780
n⟨u, in⟩ nayn un draysik zaynen zey shoyn geven,

00:14:14.780 --> 00:14:21.423
un di rusn, di rusn hobn nit gevolt ⟨shtark⟩ iberlozn dem grenets geyn, az zey zaynen gevezn.

00:14:22.189 --> 00:14:24.170
ot zaynen, ikh bin gegangen,

00:14:24.170 --> 00:14:28.130
iz, iz, mir, undz hobn zey shoyn gekont, ikh hob dokumentn gehat,

00:14:28.130 --> 00:14:30.380
un mentshn hot men umgekert krik,

00:14:30.380 --> 00:14:31.852
nit gelozn loyfn.

00:14:31.960 --> 00:14:33.923
nor ven iz men gelofn

00:14:33.923 --> 00:14:39.795
shoyn in eyn un fertsiktn, in, shoyn ⟨az,⟩ eyn un fertsikter, az der daytsh iz shoyn...

00:14:39.795 --> 00:14:42.790
hot shoyn nit geven keyn, keyn rusn.

00:14:42.810 --> 00:14:46.044
bay undz hobn, zey zaynen tselofn di ershte.

00:14:46.641 --> 00:14:48.490
alemen ibergelozt!

00:14:48.177 --> 00:14:49.270
di rusn?

00:14:48.818 --> 00:14:49.841
di rusn.

00:14:49.982 --> 00:14:51.700
iz ir vet undz dertseyln,

00:14:51.700 --> 00:14:58.890
in fertsikstn yor zenen nokh geven bay enk di rusn, un s'iz, un s'iz gekumen tsu loyfn mentshn fun Poyln?

00:14:54.572 --> 00:14:55.660
rusn.

00:14:57.373 --> 00:15:03.450
UNK gekumen tsu loyfn oto di velkhe, velkhe, velkhe zaynen, velkhe zaynen gelofn fun Poyln.

00:15:01.187 --> 00:15:03.580
fun Poyln. yo.

00:15:03.450 --> 00:15:04.758
glat gekumen.

00:15:03.580 --> 00:15:07.800
un in, un vos iz geshen nokh dem? f-...

00:15:06.705 --> 00:15:09.440
nokh de- nokh dem? gornisht!

00:15:09.440 --> 00:15:14.866
zey zaynen gegangen dem grenets tsi nit, ikh kon zikh dermit nit, ikh kon nit visn.

00:15:15.497 --> 00:15:18.880
nor UNK ikh dertseyl aykh vos zey hobn dertseylt in shul.

00:15:18.880 --> 00:15:20.970
der foter, un ikh hob mit zey oykh geredt,

00:15:19.148 --> 00:15:20.148
yo.

00:15:20.970 --> 00:15:23.793
nor zey zaynen gegangen oyf loyfn dem grenets.

00:15:24.222 --> 00:15:30.670
un bay enk zenen geblibn ale yidn oyfn ort? zey zenen geblibn in Dokshits, ale yidn?

00:15:29.655 --> 00:15:31.336
⟨n-⟩ ale yidn.

00:15:30.670 --> 00:15:33.953
un ale yidn hobn gehaltn mitn rus?

00:15:33.553 --> 00:15:36.050
yo. hert: ale yidn,

00:15:36.439 --> 00:15:42.241
ale yidn hobn gevust shoyn avos der daytsh tut. ershtns hobn mir shoyn gevust

00:15:42.241 --> 00:15:44.027
fun di tsaytungen

00:15:44.826 --> 00:15:46.845
vos in Daytshland tut zikh:

00:15:46.885 --> 00:15:51.336
me nemt arop di yidn fun di arbet, un me faryogt, un andere zetst men arayn.

00:15:51.336 --> 00:15:55.285
dos iz shoyn geven in di tsaytungen, un me leyent dokh tsaytungen, hot men gevust.

00:15:55.285 --> 00:16:00.716
nu, hobn zey gemeynt az dos iz nor, er tut di yidn ⟨un⟩ es vet azoy zayn; m'hot dokh nit gevust.

00:16:00.739 --> 00:16:04.940
az er vet geyn koylen di yidn ot azoy vi, ot v- ot vi

00:16:04.940 --> 00:16:07.224
shof, ver hot dos getrakht?

00:16:07.224 --> 00:16:09.814
mir hot men dos in Rusland gezogt

00:16:09.814 --> 00:16:12.225
in, in yor, in yor...

00:16:13.581 --> 00:16:15.696
dray un fertsik tsi fir un fertsik?

00:16:15.696 --> 00:16:19.150
plenikes zaynen antlofn, hobn zey dertseylt ⟨dortn, dertseylt⟩...

00:16:19.150 --> 00:16:20.882
zog- zogt mir

00:16:20.989 --> 00:16:22.850
mayn shvester, ⟨az ikh zog ir,⟩

00:16:22.850 --> 00:16:25.050
zogt zi, "dos makht men propagande."

00:16:26.912 --> 00:16:30.800
ir, ir farshteyt? mir hobn dos nit gegleybt.

00:16:30.962 --> 00:16:33.820
v⟨os⟩ ikh hob nit g- derzen mit di eygene oygn,

00:16:33.820 --> 00:16:35.950
hob ikh nit gegleybt.

00:16:36.143 --> 00:16:38.630
az, az dos hot zikh gornit gelozn leyenen.

00:16:38.630 --> 00:16:42.150
in der historye hob ikh dos nit geleyent. me zol azoy oyskoylen a folk?

00:16:42.218 --> 00:16:43.882
geven in Shpanye,

00:16:44.091 --> 00:16:48.080
hot er oykh ge- ge- geheysn zey shmadn, dos, yents,

00:16:48.080 --> 00:16:50.430
oder er hot nit gekoylet glaykh ale yidn.

00:16:50.689 --> 00:16:52.927
dos iz geven erger vi in Shpanye.

00:16:53.389 --> 00:16:55.420
kh'hob geleyent in Shpanye.

00:16:57.034 --> 00:16:58.327
ir farshteyt?

00:16:58.333 --> 00:17:01.840
ot dos hot zikh undz nit gegl- afile in Rusland;

00:17:01.840 --> 00:17:03.210
mir hobn gemeynt

00:17:03.210 --> 00:17:07.300
az dos makhn di rusn propagande, az me zol zey...

00:17:06.096 --> 00:17:08.260
gegn di daytshn?

00:17:07.300 --> 00:17:09.960
ye, gegn, az mir zoln zey gl- -leybn

00:17:09.960 --> 00:17:12.738
un zen az di rusn nor haltn undz oys.

00:17:14.702 --> 00:17:19.040
un ven hot zikh dos ales geendert? ven iz der daytsh arayn bay enk?

00:17:18.550 --> 00:17:25.263
iz in eyn un fertsiktn yo-... itster gib ikh f- eyn un fertsiktn yor. eyn un fertsiktn yor

00:17:25.263 --> 00:17:27.610
hot men gegebn krik.

00:17:27.730 --> 00:17:35.115
di rusn hobn bay undz in shtetl oysgeklibn etlekhe hige yugntlekhe, gegebn zey biksn hitn di shtot.

00:17:35.593 --> 00:17:37.544
un ale zaynen genumen antloyfn.

00:17:37.517 --> 00:17:42.270
di rusn zenen antlo⟨y⟩fn un zey hobn enk gelozt tsu hitn di shtot?

00:17:38.800 --> 00:17:39.990
antloyfn.

00:17:40.858 --> 00:17:42.286
hitn di shtot.

00:17:42.445 --> 00:17:47.428
iz ⟨hi-⟩ hitn di shtot iz azoy, akura- ikh bin gor geven gegn dem.

00:17:47.428 --> 00:17:52.479
⟨s'-⟩ hob ikh batrakht... hot men mir gezogt, zogt der bruder, "du darfst antloyfn."

00:17:53.937 --> 00:17:57.990
"vayle du host gearbet bay zey," zogt er, "darfst antloyfn."

00:18:00.096 --> 00:18:04.359
un ale briders un shvesters hobn demolts nokh gevoynt in shtot mit enk?

00:18:04.200 --> 00:18:05.200
⟨v-...?⟩

00:18:04.568 --> 00:18:07.730
ale briders un shve- di eltern un di...?

00:18:05.952 --> 00:18:10.090
⟨de- de-⟩ eyn bruder iz nit geven; ⟨im hot men⟩ tsugenumen in fertsiktn yor.

00:18:10.090 --> 00:18:11.860
zey hobn in fertsiktn yor shoyn,

00:18:11.860 --> 00:18:15.270
in, in eyn un fertsiktn hobn zey gemakht a mobilizatsye,

00:18:15.270 --> 00:18:17.252
hot men shoyn genumen eltere.

00:18:18.102 --> 00:18:21.670
hot men tsugenumen, un zey hobn gezogt oyf dray monat. ir veyst dokh...

00:18:21.670 --> 00:18:25.760
un m'hot tsugenumen, un oto di zaynen nit gekumen tsurik, keyn eyner nit, v-...

00:18:24.885 --> 00:18:27.697
vi azoy hot er geheysn, der bruder?

00:18:26.910 --> 00:18:30.245
der, Shmu- ⟨, z- dos, er⟩ hot geheysn Shmule Ber.

00:18:30.080 --> 00:18:32.400
un er iz keyn mol nisht tsurikgekumen?

00:18:32.057 --> 00:18:34.490
keyn mol nit. mir hobn ⟨im f-⟩...

00:18:33.280 --> 00:18:35.290
UND ⟨e⟩r veyst nisht...

00:18:34.490 --> 00:18:38.390
zint er iz avekgegangen, nit gezen, un zayn froy mit der kind

00:18:38.390 --> 00:18:39.864
iz mit undz gelofn.

00:18:40.258 --> 00:18:42.429
iz zayn kind iz geblibn lebn.

00:18:42.638 --> 00:18:44.680
itster hob ikh di kind,

00:18:44.680 --> 00:18:47.950
un di kind hot kha- itster geven, bay a bar-mitsve

00:18:47.950 --> 00:18:51.320
bin ikh geven fun dem kind's an eynikl.

00:18:53.539 --> 00:18:54.596
UNK

00:18:53.691 --> 00:18:58.055
UND er iz keyn m- ir hot keyn mol nisht gehert vos s'iz geshen mit im?

00:18:56.745 --> 00:19:00.340
mir hobn gezukht, mir hobn gefregt, ⟨he⟩...

00:19:00.340 --> 00:19:03.711
nit nor er. itster mayn, der elterer shvester's

00:19:03.711 --> 00:19:05.379
a, a, der man.

00:19:05.402 --> 00:19:09.240
iz di eltere shvester's man hot men oykh tsugenumen in yener tsayt.

00:19:08.322 --> 00:19:09.921
di eltere shvester iz...

00:19:09.240 --> 00:19:12.888
oykh, oykh nit gekumen. DORA, UNK DVORA.

00:19:09.921 --> 00:19:12.210
di eltere shvester iz geven farhey-...

00:19:12.600 --> 00:19:15.140
un zi iz shoyn geven farheyratet?

00:19:14.177 --> 00:19:16.769
un zi iz shoyn geven farheyrat for mir nokh.

00:19:16.894 --> 00:19:18.610
UND ir man hot...

00:19:17.029 --> 00:19:22.570
⟨ah,⟩ zi iz geven for, for der, for der krig iz zi geven farheyrat, un...

00:19:20.910 --> 00:19:24.010
UND ir man hobn di rusn oykh avek-...

00:19:22.615 --> 00:19:25.040
oykh tsugenu- avekgenumen,

00:19:25.040 --> 00:19:27.600
un zi hot geha- gelozn ir mit a kind,

00:19:27.600 --> 00:19:29.595
iz zi gekumen lebn bay undz

00:19:30.158 --> 00:19:33.460
in Dokshits. zi hot gelebt in Glubok frier, a ander shtot.

00:19:33.460 --> 00:19:34.944
gekumen lebn bay undz.

00:19:35.203 --> 00:19:38.780
⟨hot zi⟩ gelebt bay undz mit di kind, ⟨un zi iz⟩ avekgega- un zi iz mit UNK.

00:19:38.780 --> 00:19:43.050
iz i- nit ikh hob tsugenumen di eltern; dos iz nokh a frage nit azoy.

00:19:43.050 --> 00:19:44.934
ikh bin mitn bruder avekgegangen.

00:19:45.160 --> 00:19:51.330
UNK eyn moment. ir hot gezogt, di bruder hot gezogt, ir muzt antloyfn vayl ir hot gearbet barn rus.

00:19:50.425 --> 00:19:55.819
neyn, der bruder hot gemuzt, hobn mir gevust az mir muzn antloyfn, vayle ikh hob gearbet...

00:19:54.222 --> 00:19:57.630
ze-, iz vu zent ir antlofn? vu ahin?

00:19:56.297 --> 00:19:58.434
UNK in Rusland!

00:19:58.319 --> 00:20:01.202
in, keyn Rusland. vu?

00:19:59.419 --> 00:20:02.400
keyn Rusland. mir hobn nit gev⟨ey⟩st vuhin.

00:20:03.591 --> 00:20:04.810
gelofn.

00:20:03.700 --> 00:20:07.230
mir hobn... in vald. mir hobn nit gevust vuhin.

00:20:07.230 --> 00:20:09.810
a⟨z,⟩ mir hobn nit gevust vos s'heyst loyfn; mir hobn gemeynt

00:20:09.810 --> 00:20:13.050
az dos vet zikh bald umkern krik. s'iz dokh a milkhome.

00:20:13.050 --> 00:20:14.720
mir hobn zikh nit forgeshtelt

00:20:14.720 --> 00:20:17.318
az der rus vet lozn im geyn fray.

00:20:18.268 --> 00:20:21.200
ir farshteyt? s'iz dokh a milkhome, ⟨iz⟩ ver veyst

00:20:21.200 --> 00:20:23.932
tsi zey veln loyfn, tsi mir veln zikh umkern tsurik.

00:20:24.124 --> 00:20:26.846
hob ikh genumen, ikh hob genumen di froy oykh,

00:20:26.846 --> 00:20:30.609
mit di kind. di froy iz geven nit in ordenung; bay ir iz geven,

00:20:30.609 --> 00:20:34.929
oyf di brist hot zi gehat a UNK. m'hot dos gemakht a NITUAKH.

00:20:34.929 --> 00:20:36.811
s'iz, dos iz oykh geven a historye.

00:20:36.811 --> 00:20:42.290
un mir zaynen opgegangen tsen kilometer, hot zi genumen veynen, zogt zi, "fir mir avek tsurik.

00:20:42.838 --> 00:20:45.582
vuhin vel ikh loyfn? ikh'l shtarbn oyfn veg."

00:20:47.361 --> 00:20:50.108
hob ikh genumen a ferd... ale zaynen antlofn...

00:20:50.108 --> 00:20:54.480
ikh hob genumen a, arayn in a dorf, genumen a ferd, opgefirt ir krik

00:20:54.480 --> 00:20:57.360
tsu ir... aheym iz shoyn bay undz gornisht nit geven.

00:20:57.360 --> 00:20:59.950
ir muter iz shoyn oykh nit geven in der heym.

00:20:59.950 --> 00:21:02.542
zey zaynen ale geven bay zeyere a tokhter.

00:21:02.683 --> 00:21:07.008
un di tokhter dortn, er iz geven, er, mit ferd, hobn zey gehat a...

00:21:07.008 --> 00:21:09.177
gepakt, geforn ergets aroys.

00:21:09.177 --> 00:21:12.886
"gut", z- zo⟨g⟩n zey, "gut UNK ⟨ge⟩kumen." zog ikh, "ikh gey avek.

00:21:14.563 --> 00:21:16.300
ikh blayb do nit."

00:21:16.300 --> 00:21:21.006
zog⟨t zi, "d-"⟩ zogn zey take, "du gey avek, vayle tsulib dir konen mir oykh laydn."

00:21:21.006 --> 00:21:23.467
ir farshteyt dokh, vayle kh'hob gearbet bay di rusn.

00:21:23.187 --> 00:21:26.190
zey hobn moyre gehat az zey veln laydn vayl,

00:21:24.925 --> 00:21:29.950
az zey veln laydn tsulib mir, vayle ikh, vayle ikh hob gearbet bay di rusn.

00:21:26.190 --> 00:21:29.171
vayl ir zent geven a vikhtike perzon.

00:21:29.950 --> 00:21:31.570
bin ikh avekgegangen

00:21:31.570 --> 00:21:33.570
un hob ikh keynem nit gefunen.

00:21:33.582 --> 00:21:37.350
keynem nit. ale zaynen shoyn geven avek in vald.

00:21:39.302 --> 00:21:43.520
mit mir iz nokh ge⟨zo-⟩ a, gekumen eyner a khaver mayner.

00:21:43.520 --> 00:21:46.977
zogt er... er l- zayn shve- zayn shvester ⟨iz⟩ avekgelofn, mit alts...

00:21:46.977 --> 00:21:48.926
"mir vel'n geyn, tsuzamen gey⟨n." zog ikh,⟩

00:21:48.926 --> 00:21:51.871
"itster geyn konen ⟨mir nit." s'iz⟩ zeyer fintster geven.

00:21:51.871 --> 00:21:55.361
zog ikh, "kum tsu undz in shtub," vu mir hobn ⟨a,⟩ gelebt.

00:21:55.367 --> 00:21:59.000
mir zaynen avekgegangen oyfn veg un mir hobn zikh avekgeleygt

00:21:59.000 --> 00:22:02.700
in di groz. ⟨mir hobn shoyn...⟩ un, un dortn iz shoyn geven daytshn,

00:22:02.700 --> 00:22:06.262
nor di zelner nokh mitn fuln parad iz nit arayn.

00:22:07.264 --> 00:22:11.630
un mir hobn dortn gemakht bizn a zeyger dray ⟨in d-⟩ far tog,

00:22:11.630 --> 00:22:15.172
un s'iz dokh geven, dray iz shoyn likhtik vayle s'iz geven zumer.

00:22:15.195 --> 00:22:16.758
s'iz geven IYUN'.

00:22:17.001 --> 00:22:22.175
iz zaynen mir avekgegangen durkh di velder. mir zaynen gekumen in vald un avekgegangen in vald.

00:22:22.350 --> 00:22:25.258
mir zaynen, i⟨ts-⟩ vil ikh aykh nokh dertseyln:

00:22:25.258 --> 00:22:30.106
geyendik oyfn veg gegenen mir on forn krik tsvey furn mentshn.

00:22:30.771 --> 00:22:33.296
er git a kuk: zayn shvester

00:22:33.572 --> 00:22:35.810
mit, mit a khosn, hot zi gehat,

00:22:35.810 --> 00:22:38.490
un nokh yugntlekhe forn krik. zey zogn, "vos,

00:22:38.490 --> 00:22:41.666
⟨m-...⟩" in vald iz nit azoy geven gut.

00:22:41.841 --> 00:22:46.324
"vos ⟨zoln mir⟩ dokh lign hungern?" zogn zey, "vos vet zayn mit alemen vet zayn mit undz."

00:22:46.431 --> 00:22:47.850
un zaynen avek krik.

00:22:47.850 --> 00:22:49.263
ikh bin avek foroys.

00:22:49.263 --> 00:22:52.080
kh'bin gekumen in vald ersht bay nakht.

00:22:52.080 --> 00:22:56.426
kh'hob getrofn tsvey shvester dortn un dem bruder,

00:22:56.426 --> 00:22:59.480
un ful khevre, a fule vald.

00:22:59.480 --> 00:23:03.240
zey zogn az der foter mit di muter iz oykh do.

00:23:03.240 --> 00:23:07.890
zog ikh, "vos ⟨hot ir zey⟩ geton?" ikh aleyn trakht,

00:23:08.318 --> 00:23:12.900
"vos... v-..." ⟨az⟩ ikh hob dos nit forgeshtel-... ir farshteyt? azoy nit...

00:23:12.900 --> 00:23:16.040
UNK zog⟨ ikh⟩ zey, "vu zaynen zey?" zogn zey, "do in a dorf."

00:23:16.401 --> 00:23:21.380
in a dorf gekumen. ⟨iz⟩ bald zaynen gekumen di, di makht

00:23:21.953 --> 00:23:24.242
un hobn undz gezogt azoy:

00:23:24.282 --> 00:23:27.274
"fun danet muzt ir geyn foroys. far vos?

00:23:27.274 --> 00:23:30.300
vayle mir raysn oyfet di brikn fun,

00:23:30.340 --> 00:23:32.142
fun BEREZINA."

00:23:32.142 --> 00:23:34.790
tsvey groyse brikn dortn.

00:23:34.862 --> 00:23:38.960
zaynen mir geven bay yene tsvey brikn dortn i- in vald.

00:23:38.960 --> 00:23:40.883
"muzt ir ibergeyn di brikn,

00:23:40.883 --> 00:23:43.550
vayle anit blaybn mir ale do."

00:23:43.550 --> 00:23:47.228
un zey hobn shoyn undz, nit gekont fun undz antloyfn.

00:23:47.228 --> 00:23:49.760
geven der predsyedatel fun ⟨RAY-,⟩

00:23:49.932 --> 00:23:51.850
Vilenski, oykh a yid,

00:23:52.108 --> 00:23:55.106
⟨n-⟩ nor er iz geven der firer fun di rusn bay undz.

00:23:55.382 --> 00:24:02.660
iz hot er, un tsug- mir, zaynen mir ale avekgegangen, mit khevre, mi- geven a por ferd, etlekhe ferd iz geven,

00:24:02.660 --> 00:24:04.236
mir zaynen ibergeforn.

00:24:04.495 --> 00:24:08.336
ikh zog tsu undzerike, "kum zen di mame mitn tatn.

00:24:08.494 --> 00:24:11.250
me darf zey glaykh nemen mit."

00:24:11.447 --> 00:24:16.267
mir ⟨zaynen⟩ avek zey nemen, hobn mir shoyn kumendik, hobn mir zey keynem nit gefunen.

00:24:16.476 --> 00:24:19.740
ale zaynen shoyn geven vu antlofn.

00:24:19.740 --> 00:24:24.244
mir hobn genumen undzer mishpokhe un mir zaynen gelofn. mir hobn gehat tate-mame,

00:24:24.244 --> 00:24:25.683
tsvey kinder,

00:24:26.382 --> 00:24:30.240
pitslekh tsvey yorike tsi... ⟨ikh⟩ gedenk nit azoy gen⟨oy⟩...

00:24:30.533 --> 00:24:34.256
un mir zaynen aleyn geven tsvey brider un nokh di shvester,

00:24:34.667 --> 00:24:40.510
un nokh bay mi- a! di shvegerin vos iz, vos ⟨iz di, funem⟩ dem bruder's man.

00:24:38.194 --> 00:24:40.830
un vu iz geven di andere shvester?

00:24:40.510 --> 00:24:41.400
vos?

00:24:40.830 --> 00:24:43.280
vu iz geven di andere shvestern?

00:24:42.666 --> 00:24:46.659
di andere shvester zaynen geven in vald. di andere shvester zaynen geven yingere.

00:24:46.716 --> 00:24:48.771
dos iz di eltere, DVORA,

00:24:47.987 --> 00:24:48.987
yo.

00:24:48.771 --> 00:24:51.440
iz zi shoyn geven mit a man mit a kind, ⟨iz...⟩

00:24:51.440 --> 00:24:55.100
zey zaynen shoyn nit geven; zey zaynen geven ⟨in shaykhes⟩ tsu di eltere,

00:24:55.100 --> 00:24:57.864
un yene zaynen geven yingere fun mir a sakh.

00:24:57.440 --> 00:24:59.780
zenen zey ⟨n-⟩ avek in vald arayn?

00:24:58.309 --> 00:25:01.600
zaynen zey, zaynen mir ale in vald. zey hobn zey gebrakht,

00:25:01.600 --> 00:25:03.568
zaynen zey gekumen in vald avek.

00:25:03.861 --> 00:25:05.750
do iz dokh nit nor zey;

00:25:05.750 --> 00:25:07.747
a sakh yugntlekhe

00:25:07.747 --> 00:25:09.770
zaynen mir geven in vald.

00:25:09.598 --> 00:25:11.960
vi lang zent ir geven in vald?

00:25:11.337 --> 00:25:15.710
in vald zaynen mir geven efsher etlekhe teg. nit lang, vayl

00:25:15.710 --> 00:25:17.480
der daytsh hot shoyn undz...

00:25:17.480 --> 00:25:22.046
un bald hot der daytsh genumen dem vald bombirn mit, fun der heykh.

00:25:22.052 --> 00:25:23.900
m'hot shoyn gemuzt loyfn.

00:25:23.900 --> 00:25:26.890
hobn mir genumen di eltern. ale zaynen tselofn fun undz.

00:25:26.890 --> 00:25:27.960
hob ikh dokh gezogt,

00:25:27.960 --> 00:25:30.630
vi zey hobn derhert eltere mentshn un kinder,

00:25:30.630 --> 00:25:33.010
iz di yugnt antlofn fun undz.

00:25:33.915 --> 00:25:36.963
zey hobn moyre gehat az m'vet khapn shneler?

00:25:35.299 --> 00:25:39.290
⟨a- a- nu,⟩ zey hobn moyre gehat, ⟨es⟩, az s'iz ferd, mir veln tsunemen di ferd bay zey.

00:25:39.290 --> 00:25:42.280
ir veyst dokh ⟨az b-⟩ kleyne kinder, pitslekh tsvey yorike,

00:25:42.280 --> 00:25:44.240
un, un, un eltere mentshn. d-

00:25:44.240 --> 00:25:47.200
der foter iz dokh geven in di zekhtsiker, in di zekhtsiker yorn,

00:25:47.200 --> 00:25:49.518
oder zaynen shoyn geven eltere mentshn!

00:25:50.588 --> 00:25:53.940
zaynen zey tselofn fun undz. f- tselofn fun undz...

00:25:53.940 --> 00:25:55.883
hobn mir zikh genumen, zog ikh...

00:25:55.883 --> 00:25:59.677
ikh bin shoyn geven der firer, zog ikh, "hot keyn moyre nit. mir geyen foroys."

00:25:59.751 --> 00:26:04.836
zaynen mir gegangen tsu fus efsher tsen kilometer, fuftsn kilometer.

00:26:04.836 --> 00:26:08.820
di muter hot nit gekont mer geyn.

00:26:09.235 --> 00:26:12.418
zaynen mir a bisl geshtanen, avek, opgevart...

00:26:12.542 --> 00:26:18.141
nokh in a shtetl, nor ikh ⟨g-⟩ ale shtetlekh ge- kon ikh nit ge- s'iz geven shtetlekh, ikh gedenk nit

00:26:18.141 --> 00:26:20.540
vi hobn zey geheysn, nor in Rusland shoyn,

00:26:20.540 --> 00:26:22.200
nokh alts Vaysrusland.

00:26:22.200 --> 00:26:27.180
un gegangen zaynen mir, hobn mir shoyn gevust loytn, loyt der karte az mir geyn

00:26:27.180 --> 00:26:28.820
in shtot Vitebsk.

00:26:28.820 --> 00:26:32.690
Vitebsk, dos iz oykh a groyse shtot in Vaysrusland.

00:26:33.450 --> 00:26:34.810
Vitebsk.

00:26:33.771 --> 00:26:37.630
un ir volt, ir hot gevolt geyn in der rikhtung fun Vitebsk?

00:26:37.630 --> 00:26:40.520
ir hot gevolt f- onkumen tsu Vitebsk?

00:26:40.065 --> 00:26:44.239
mir hobn gevolt onkum- onkumen ergets, onkumen ergets.

00:26:44.239 --> 00:26:46.421
un mir zaynen ⟨d⟩okh al-... es-...

00:26:44.250 --> 00:26:48.590
ir hot gehat es- ir hot gehat mit zikh esn, trinken?

00:26:47.710 --> 00:26:49.678
keyn zakh nit!

00:26:49.937 --> 00:26:53.450
ikh hob... o! vos iz geven? ikh hob gehat gelt.

00:26:53.450 --> 00:26:55.830
zey zaynen gelofn on gelt.

00:26:57.936 --> 00:26:59.780
zey hobn alts azoy oyfn gas

00:26:59.780 --> 00:27:02.670
ibergelozt un m'hot gemakht a tuml, "der daytsh geyt!"

00:27:02.670 --> 00:27:06.470
un alts ibergelozt un antlofn. alts iz geblibn bay undz ofn.

00:27:06.475 --> 00:27:10.930
⟨n- nokh dem⟩ zaynen di poyerim gegangen mit di zek un m'hot genumen fun di yidn.

00:27:11.740 --> 00:27:16.640
nit nor, ⟨s'iz, s'iz,⟩ dernokh dem di historye vos di partizaner hobn mir dertseylt;

00:27:16.640 --> 00:27:18.790
ikh bin derbay shoyn nit geven.

00:27:18.790 --> 00:27:22.551
UNK ikh bin gekumen krik... do iz do a frage, ikh bin gekumen krik, vel ikh aykh zogn...

00:27:23.535 --> 00:27:28.828
n⟨u,⟩ mir zaynen gelofn. es, vos ikh hob g- ongegegnt, es fort a last-oyto.

00:27:29.290 --> 00:27:33.657
a last-oyto. "T-" zog ikh im, "TOVARISHCH"... ikh hob opgeshtelt im.

00:27:33.657 --> 00:27:36.810
er hot zikh opgeshtelt. zog ikh, "fir mir, undz tsu oto do."

00:27:36.810 --> 00:27:40.090
hot er undz ibergevorfn mistome tsvantsik kilometer.

00:27:40.191 --> 00:27:43.760
zogt er, mer hot er keyn benzin nit, un undz geheysn geyn.

00:27:43.760 --> 00:27:47.981
mir zaynen arop un mir zaynen vi es iz farkrokhn keyn Vitebsk.

00:27:48.308 --> 00:27:51.000
oyfn, oyf a, nokh in tsvey teg arum... ikh,

00:27:51.000 --> 00:27:54.450
kh'kon aykh punkt di sho nit zogn, vayl⟨e do-...⟩

00:27:54.450 --> 00:27:55.620
s'iz a shvere zakh.

00:27:55.620 --> 00:27:57.380
kumendik in Vitebsk

00:27:57.640 --> 00:27:59.844
hobn mir shoyn derzen mentshn.

00:28:06.988 --> 00:28:09.727
dortn hobn mir shoyn getrofn i shtetlshe...

00:28:09.727 --> 00:28:12.418
nor vemen trefstu? yugntlekhe.

00:28:12.418 --> 00:28:15.808
mir hobn getrofn tsvey mishpokhes, eyner a shnayder,

00:28:16.230 --> 00:28:18.896
 un Pildusn, un nokh a mishpokhe.

00:28:19.054 --> 00:28:22.500
un ikh hob gehat a rukzak oyfn hant, mit a mantl.

00:28:22.598 --> 00:28:25.680
nem ikh un leyg bay im avek oyfn fur

00:28:25.680 --> 00:28:27.720
dem mantl mitn rukzak

00:28:27.720 --> 00:28:28.734
un gey avek.

00:28:28.791 --> 00:28:31.721
m⟨ir hobn zey⟩... ikh bin gekumen, er iz nit geven.

00:28:33.340 --> 00:28:35.858
ir farshteyt? ⟨zaynen nit geven; er hot⟩ tsugenumen alts.

00:28:35.858 --> 00:28:38.538
hob ikh, bin ikh geblibn ot azoy vi ikh bin itster.

00:28:39.355 --> 00:28:41.138
nor farfaln! me geyt.

00:28:42.139 --> 00:28:50.486
zaynen gegangen, gekumen in Vitebsk, zog ikh... a kuk geton vos s'tut zikh in Vitebsk, mit mentshn oyfn gas, do, dortn, ful in ale gasn...

00:28:50.543 --> 00:28:52.800
zog ikh, "do iz keyn ort nit."

00:28:53.597 --> 00:28:56.380
ikh farshtey az do iz keyn ort nit.

00:28:56.380 --> 00:28:58.010
zog ikh, "kumt."

00:28:58.778 --> 00:29:03.470
zey hobn nokh ongehoybn reydn, "efsher do..." un andere zogn, "m'vet undz gebn arbet."

00:29:03.470 --> 00:29:07.500
zog ikh, "vos far a arbet? der daytsh iz hinter undz!

00:29:08.548 --> 00:29:10.280
vu iz di arbet?"

00:29:10.280 --> 00:29:11.650
ikh hob shoyn gezen

00:29:11.650 --> 00:29:14.010
az Rusland hot keyn armey nit.

00:29:14.404 --> 00:29:18.600
ikh bin dokh gegangen, ze ikh dokh vos s'tut zikh: soldatn loyfn un der loyft...

00:29:18.600 --> 00:29:20.080
s'iz nito keyn frage!

00:29:20.080 --> 00:29:22.980
in a vald gefinstu dortn, dortn iz soldatn a bisele.

00:29:23.010 --> 00:29:26.362
zey zaynen gegn dem daytsh? mit di tankes?

00:29:27.195 --> 00:29:30.429
undz vel'mir vayter geyn oyf di nekste kasete.

00:29:29.085 --> 00:29:34.023
ikh bin, ikh ⟨bin⟩ shoyn geven a militer-man oykh, un ikh hob gezen vos s'tut zikh di lage.

00:29:34.097 --> 00:29:36.290
ikh bin shoyn bay zey oyf kursn geven.

00:29:36.290 --> 00:29:38.900
ikh, ikh hob shoyn gezen di lage, vos s'tut zikh.

00:29:38.844 --> 00:29:42.810
undz vel'mir endi- undz vel'mir vayter geyn oyf di nekste kasete, OKAY?

00:29:42.130 --> 00:29:44.436
s'iz, es iz shoyn nokh a kasete?

00:29:42.810 --> 00:29:45.960
yo. yo, yo. yo, yo. bald.

00:29:44.712 --> 00:29:46.020
geendi-...
